      <title>贝恩、Solamere 私募股权金融家正在举办 Haley 筹款活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/bain-solamere-private-equity-titans-to-fundraise-for-haley</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，贝恩资本 (Bain Capital) 高级顾问保罗·埃杰利 (Paul Edgerley) 和 Solamere Capital 联合创始人斯宾塞·兹威克 (Spencer Zwick) 是为妮基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 举办筹款活动的捐助者之一，这位共和党总统候选人越来越受到华尔街的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/bain-solamere-private-equity-titans-to-fundraise-for-haley</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 18:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州预计收入暴跌将缺口 680 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/california-projects-68-billion-shortfall-on-income-tax-plunge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州预算顾问表示，由于所得税收入大幅下降，该州下一财年可能面临 680 亿美元的赤字，这将是连续第二年出现赤字，这可能导致关键安全网项目的削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/california-projects-68-billion-shortfall-on-income-tax-plunge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对哥伦比亚特区选举阻碍案中的豁免权丧失提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/trump-appeals-immunity-loss-in-dc-election-obstruction-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 要求停止针对他的联邦选举阻挠案，同时他对法官的裁决提出上诉，该裁决剥夺了他因推翻 2020 年总统选举而获得刑事指控的全面豁免权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/trump-appeals-immunity-loss-in-dc-election-obstruction-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登弹劾调查将于下周众议院投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/biden-impeachment-inquiry-set-for-house-vote-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党人周四迈出了一步，正式授权对总统乔·拜登进行与其家族商业交易有关的弹劾调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/biden-impeachment-inquiry-set-for-house-vote-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛、宾夕法尼亚大学校长在强烈反对后收回种族灭绝答案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/harvard-penn-heads-walk-back-genocide-answers-as-backlash-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在商界领袖和政界人士的一连串批评之后，哈佛大学和宾夕法尼亚大学的校长被迫发表声明，澄清他们对美国国会反犹太主义听证会的回应，而这些批评几乎没有减弱的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/harvard-penn-heads-walk-back-genocide-answers-as-backlash-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 13:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
