      <title>战争和气候加剧痛苦，非洲饥饿危机加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/africa-s-hunger-crisis-deepens-as-war-climate-pile-on-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气候变化和乌克兰战争加剧了该地区的不安全局势，非洲有超过 2.8 亿人正在挨饿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/africa-s-hunger-crisis-deepens-as-war-climate-pile-on-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 13:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
